---
description: Private methods are prefixed with `_`
globs: **/*.cs
alwaysApply: true
---

# Naming rule: `private` methods use `_` prefix

- Rename any `private` method (including `private static` / `private async`) to start with `_`.
- Example:
  - ❌ `private static void PrintJson(...)`
  - ✅ `private static void _PrintJson(...)`

